<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id5fd70148-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s21"><num value="21">§ 21.</num><heading> Mineral lands reserved</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In all cases lands valuable for minerals shall be reserved from sale, except as otherwise expressly directed by law.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id5fd70149-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(R.S. § 2318.)</sourceCredit>
